title.narrative: Solomon Islands Inland Revenue Division II

description.narrative: This activity will focus on continuing to strengthen the Solomon Island Government's revenue base and building the Solomon Islands Inland Revenue Division's local capacity and capability. We will provide funding for up to nine technical advisors, systems upgrades, technical training and leadership development. This will enable ongoing capacity supplementation; improved local capacity and capability development; and improved voluntary tax compliance and enforcement.
